Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Sta. Cruz Elementary School in the Municipality of Pandan, Province of Antique, to Vidal Gileto Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 338
An Act Changing the Name of the Sta. Cruz Elementary School in the Municipality of Pandan, Province of Antique, to Vidal Gileto Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the Sta. Cruz Elementary School in the Municipality of Pandan, Province of Antique, is changed to Vidal Gileto Memorial School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: February 10, 1983
